name: ABCD
description:
At ABCD HEAD START, we prepare your child for preschool and kindergarten using activities and experiences that develop their cognitive and emotional skills. We also have programs for pregnant women and children to fit the needs of your family.


Head Start is a family development program that offers comprehensive services for your child as well as your entire family. Part of a highly successful national program, ABCD Head Start has locations throughout Boston, Everett, Malden, and Medford.
